# SIF: routine-level whitelist. Only subprograms whose names match an entry
# below are instrumented. The Fortran matcher uses std::regex_match (full
# string) against the bare subprogram name, so a plain literal identifier
# matches exactly that name. Use the `#` kleene-star wildcard for prefix or
# suffix matches.
BEGIN_INCLUDE_LIST
keep_routine
END_INCLUDE_LIST
